        <p>&ldquo;Our new circular frame mirrors the shape of the Golden Record, but our tribute goes beyond the literal. Like our wayfarer, our circle frame has mass appeal. That is, we designed the frame’s shape and fit to be as inclusive as possible, much in the way the Golden Record tries to reflect the vast diversity of life on Earth.&rdquo;</p>
        <p>&ldquo;After two years of prototyping, we feel confident that Voyager &lsquo;best flatters the most people.&rsquo; The non-gendered design is appropriate for all demographic cohorts, and the frame tones were chosen with all ethnicities in mind. With Voyager, we haven’t changed our position on offering customers a universal frame – we just now offer one that is round.&rdquo; – Robert Denning, Creative Director</p>
